item.title: CVE-2016-10594|2024-09-16T22:29:58.195Z -- hackerone -- ipip%20node%20module
item.description: ipip is a Node.js module to query geolocation information for an IP or domain, based on database by ipip.net. ipip downloads data resources over HTTP, which leaves it vulnerable to MITM attacks.
